In index.html, find all CSS rules for input, .add-input, .lf-add-input, .m-input, .m-textarea, and .m-select and make sure they all have font-size: 16px on mobile. Add this to the mobile media query (@media(max-width:680px)):
input, textarea, select, .add-input, .lf-add-input, .m-input, .m-textarea, .m-select {
  font-size: 16px !important;
}Then commit and push: git add -A && git commit -m "Fix iOS input zoom" && git push

